#: Game.Levels.ReflectionWorld.L12_AbelianSubgroupsAreNormal
msgid "Abelian Subgroups are Normal"
msgstr ""

#. §0: `op_assoc a b c`
#. §1: `(a * b) * c = a * (b * c)`
#: Game.Documentation.Group.Group
#: Game.Documentation.Group.Group
#: Game.Documentation.Group.Group
#: Game.Levels.GroupWorld.L03_LeftInverseCancellation
#: Game.Levels.GroupWorld.L04_LeftCancellation
