#: Game.Levels.GroupWorld.L03_LeftInverseCancellation
msgid "For this level, you'll have to use all three group axioms. As always, click on §0 -> §1 to see what you've unlocked. After this level, you'll be able to use this fact in all future proofs without redoing the steps. We will attempt to prove that, if we have an expression §2, we can multiply by §3 on the left to cancel out the §4.\n"
"\n"
"A quirk of §5 is that, for some hypothesis §6, §7 will only attempt to replace an §8 with a §9. If we wanted to do the opposite, we'd have to reverse the hypothesis. We can do this by typing a §10 (\\\\l) right before §11.\n"
"\n"
"For the rest of the levels in this world, I'll provide a complete set of steps given to you behind hints in case you get stuck. However, I'd like it if you used them as little as possible, because it's not great for learning if you're just copying down my proof without thinking about it first."
msgstr ""

